In the case of stress-free interfaces, Kocarkova et al.37 calculated the evolution of the film thickness considering an extensional flow in the film, assumed to be uniform and axisymmetric. They observed an exponential thinning, from which the dimensionless lifetime can be shown to be:15\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
