In the limit of small Bond numbers, no simple model exists for the bubble lifetime because in this limit the drainage is driven by capillary forces which also induce surface deformations. The model of Howell39, considers this case but assumes an extensional flow, which leads to17\documentclass[12pt]{minimal}
				\usepackage{amsmath}
